milestones.description: Odumbe and Thomas Odoyo's 105-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 84 between Odumbe and Alpesh Vadher
This is the highest match aggregate (459) involving teams South Africa & Kenya in ODIs
Odumbe has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (40) for KENYA, going past Steve Tikolo
